{"tid":1945753,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《安眠書店》Mark Blum死於武漢肺炎 享年69歲","createTime":"2020-03-27T09:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T01:34:00.000Z","uid":130626,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4930a08524beb258f28ce7d9650d8752e9d5d151","tid":1945753,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T09:09:40.000Z","msg":"美國資深男演員Mark Blum，今日傳來離世消息，並獲證實成為首位死於武漢肺炎的荷李活影星，享年69歲。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎肆虐全球，還嚴重衝擊演藝界，繼四度奪得東尼獎的81歲美國劇作家麥克納利（Terrence McNally）感染武漢肺炎後逝世，荷李活電影演員協會近日亦發聲明，公佈演技派男星Mark Blum死於武肺的噩耗。<br />\n<br />\nMark Blum從1970年代就開始入行，參演數十套影視作品，當中較為人熟識有跟麥當娜（Madonna）合作的1985年電影《神秘約會》（Desperately Seeking Susan），Mark亦活躍於電視圈和舞台劇界，還在《安眠書店》（You）飾演劇中關鍵角色的書店老闆Mr. Mooney。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200327/large/1585274227_7a44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200327%2Flarge%2F1585274227_7a44.jpg&h=b186d048&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200327/large/1585274268_4e21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200327%2Flarge%2F1585274268_4e21.jpg&h=24a93bf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200327/XV2EEHOLLPHRPYKVOQSETWSA7M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200327%2FXV2EEHOLLPHRPYKVOQSETWSA7M%2F&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=c8ca7c0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200327%2FXV2EEHOLLPHRPYKVOQSETWSA7M%2F&h=06670989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200327/XV2EEHOLLPHRPYKVOQSETWSA7M/</a>"},{"pid":"8ca14650bab637e2be516711a4e13b126c40bee3","tid":1945753,"uid":66839,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"repl